{
  "texts": [
    "Third, does providing people with a label of the source of reappraisal (GPT-4 or humans) impact their evaluation of the quality of reappraisal?",
    "Fourth, what linguistic features distinguish GPT-4 reappraisals from human reappraisals, and are these features related to reappraisal quality?",
    "To answer these questions, we provided both humans and GPT with reappraisal training, and compared their utility both in response to vignettes (Study 1) and in real-time interactions, rated in terms of quality by the recipients of the reappraisal (Study 2).",
    "In Study 3 we incentivized some of the human participants to improve their reappraisals.",
    "In Study 4, we provided raters with labels of the source of reappraisal (GPT-4 or humans) and examined the impact on their evaluations."
  ]
}